Text.val: Any Return on investmenst calculation start with the values at the start of the day. Read the de closing values of the day
before. So every start date is decremented one day to get a correct starting position on the reported start date,
Special attention for first mutation dates (now handled identical to normal start dates and the start of persistent calculation
no mutations and (price-changes) are assumed to have happened. So the 1-1-2018 endvalues are reported as 31-12-2017 values
Flow monitor melding bij errors die niet kunnen worden vertaald naar responses zodat ze toch terug te vinden zijn.
Warnings / Info should be excluded as errors.

SQL_STMT_U.val: select positionDate, portfolioValue, cashValue, histValue, accruedInterest, cashCorrection, portfolioCorrection, historicCorrection, totalCosts, directCosts, indirectCosts from ( select m.positionDate , (select sum(pb.value) from pc_portfolio_base pb where pb.pere_id = ~1 and pb.calc_date = positionDate) as portfolioValue , (select sum(ab.value) from pc_account_base ab inner join rekeningen r on r.re_id = ab.account_id where ab.pere_id = ~1 and ab.calc_date = positionDate and r.re_securities_re_id is not null) as cashValue , (select sum(hb.value) from PC_HISTORIC_PORTFOLIO_BASE hb where hb.pere_id = ~1 and hb.calc_date = positionDate) as histValue , (select sum(pa.amount*pa.factor) from pc_portfolio_amount pa inner join pc_portfolio_base pb on pb.id=pa.pcpb_id and pb.calc_date = positionDate where pb.pere_id = ~1 and pa.pcca_id = ~5 ) as accruedInterest , (select sum(ta.amount) from pc_transaction_amount ta inner join pc_transaction_base tb on tb.id=ta.pctb_id and tb.transaction_date = positionDate where tb.pere_id = ~1 and ta.pcca_id = ~4 and ta.be_id is null) as cashCorrection , (select sum(round(ta.amount,2)) from ha.pcca_id = ~4) as historicCorrection , (select decode(:9, 1, (select sum(cost_amount) from ( select round(sum(-pa.amount*pa.factor),2) cost_amount from pc_portfolio_amount pa inner join pc_portfolio_base pb on pb.id = pa.pcpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = pa.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join inner join pc_transaction_base tb on tb.id = ta.pctb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ta.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~6 and tb.pere_id = ~1 and tb.transaction_date = positionDate union select sum(ha.value) from pc_historic_amounts ha inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base hb on hb.id = ha.phpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ha.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join nvl(sum(costs),0) amount from ( select nvl(round(sum(-pa.amount*pa.factor),2),0) costs from pc_portfolio_amount pa inner join pc_portfolio_base pb on pb.id = pa.pcpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = pa.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~6 and pb.pere_id = ~1 and prc.prc_id = ~7 and pb.calc_date = positionDate union select nvl(sum(ta.amount),0) from pc_transaction_amount ta inner join pc_transaction_base tb on tb.id = ta.pctb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ta.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~6 and tb.pere_id = ~1 and prc.prc_id = ~7 and tb.transaction_date = positionDate union select nvl(sum(ha.value),0) from pc_historic_amounts ha inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base hb on hb.id = ha.phpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ha.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~6 and hb.pere_id = ~1 and prc.prc_id = ~7 and hb.calc_date = positionDate)),0) from dual) DirectCosts , (select decode(:10, 1, (select nvl(sum(costs),0) amount join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~6 and pb.pere_id = ~1 and tb.pere_id = ~1 and prc.prc_id = ~8 and tb.transaction_date = positionDate union select nvl(sum(ha.value),0) from pc_historic_amounts ha inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base hb on hb.id = ha.phpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ha.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~6 and hb.pere_id = ~1 and prc.prc_id = ~8 and hb.calc_date = positionDate)), 0) from dual) InDirectCosts FROM ( SELECT CALC_DATE as positionDate FROM PC_ACCOUNT_BASE AB WHERE SQL_STMT_U.val:
select (select sum(pb.value) from pc_portfolio_base pb where pb.pere_id = ~1 and pb.calc_date = to_date(~2, 'YYYY-MM-DD')) as portfolioValue , (select sum(ab.value) from pc_account_base ab inner join rekeningen r on r.re_id = ab.account_id where ab.pere_id = ~1 and ab.calc_date = to_date(~2, 'YYYY-MM-DD') and r.re_securities_re_id is not null) as accountValue , (select sum(hb.value) from pc_historic_portfolio_base hb where hb.pere_id = ~1 and hb.calc_date = to_date(~2, 'YYYY-MM-DD')) as historicValue , (select sum(pa.amount*pa.factor) from pc_portfolio_amount pa inner join pc_portfolio_base pb on pb.id=pa.pcpb_id and pb.calc_date = to_date(~2, 'YYYY-MM-DD') where pb.pere_id = ~1 and pa.pcca_id = ~3 ) as accruedInterest
FROM dual

select s.type, sum(s.amount) amount, round(sum(s.amount*(to_date( ~3 , 'YYYY-MM-DD')-s.calc_date+1)/(to_date( ~3 , 'YYYY-MM-DD')-to_date( ~2 , 'YYYY-MM-DD')+1)),2) weigthed_amount from ( select decode(nvl(a.be_id,0),0, 'S', 'I') as type, round(a.amount,2) amount, b.transaction_date calc_date from pc_transaction_amount a inner join pc_transaction_base b on b.id = a.pctb_id inner join pc_category c on c.id = a.pcca_id where b.pere_id = ~1 and c.code = 204 and b.transaction_date between to_date(~2 , 'YYYY-MM-DD') and to_date( ~3 , 'YYYY-MM-DD') union all select 'I', round(a.value,2) amount, b.calc_date calc_date from pc_historic_amounts a inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base b on b.id = a.phpb_id inner join pc_category c on c.id = a.pcca_id where b.pere_id = ~1 and c.code = 204 and b.calc_date between to_date(~2 , 'YYYY-MM-DD') and to_date( ~3 , 'YYYY-MM-DD')) s group by type

SQL_STMT_U.val: select sum(costs), prc_id from ( select round(sum(-pa.amount*pa.factor),2) costs, prc.prc_id from pc_portfolio_amount pa inner join pc_portfolio_base pb on pb.id = pa.pcpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = pa.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~1 and pb.pere_id = ~2 and pb.calc_date between to_date(~3,'YYYY-MM-DD') and to_date(~4,'YYYY-MM-DD') group by prc.prc_id union select sum(ta.amount), prc.prc_id from pc_transaction_amount ta inner join pc_transaction_base tb on tb.id = ta.pctb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ta.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~1 and tb.pere_id = ~2 and tb.transaction_date between to_date(~3,'YYYY-MM-DD') and to_date(~4,'YYYY-MM-DD') group by prc.prc_id union select sum(ha.value), prc.prc_id from pc_historic_amounts ha inner join pc_historic_portfolio_base hb on hb.id = ha.phpb_id inner join pc_category pc on pc.id = ha.pcca_id inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on prk.prk_perf_calc_cat = pc.code inner join performance_report_class prc on prc.prc_id = prk.prk_perf_rap_cat where prc.vbg_id = ~1 and hb.pere_id = ~2 and hb.calc_date between to_date(~3,'YYYY-MM-DD') and to_date(~4,'YYYY-MM-DD') group by prc.prc_id) group by prc_id

select max(my_date) from ( select max (calc_date) as my_date from pc_portfolio_base b inner join performance_report r on r.id = b.pere_id and r.ppr_id = ~1 union all select max (calc_date) as my_date from pc_account_base b inner join performance_report r on r.id = b.pere_id and r.ppr_id = ~1)
